nodes.text: Cylo's whale fleet was a massive fleet made out of organic whale-ships that was led by Doctor Cylo himself and held Cylo's research base. Cylo planned to hijack the Executor, which was under construction over Kuat, but his plans ultimately failed and Darth Vader used the Force and convince the whale-ships to fly into a star in the Kuat system, thus destroying the entire whale-ship fleet.
